 (B), struck out “after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 1992","children":[],"tail":",” before “mean any” and “by the Farm Credit System Assistance Board under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2278a–6"},"text":"section 2278a–6 of this title","children":[],"tail":" or” before “by the Farm Credit System Insurance Corporation”, and struck out former subpar. (B) which read as follows: “during the period beginning on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-01-06"},"text":"January 6, 1988","children":[],"tail":", and ending "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 1992","children":[],"tail":", mean any noncompliance by a System institution, as determined by the Farm Credit Administration in consultation with the Assistance Board, with any term or condition imposed on the institution by the Assistance Board under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2278a–6"},"text":"section 2278a–6 of this title","children":[],"tail":"; and”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1992—Par. (4)(C). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/552"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–552","children":[],"tail":" added subpar. (C)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1991—Par. (3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/237"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–237","children":[],"tail":" substituted “part E” for “part D”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1988—Par. (3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/233/s207/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–233, § 207(d)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Financial Assistance Corporation” for “Capital Corporation”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (4). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/233/s203"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–233, § 203","children":[],"tail":", amended par. (4) generally. Prior to amendment, par. (4) read as follows: “the term ‘unsafe or unsound practice’ shall have the meaning given to it by the Farm Credit Administration by regulations, rule, or order.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"iddcd2336c-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"iddcd2336d-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1991 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/237"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–237","children":[],"tail":" effective as if included in the provision of the Food, Agriculture, Conservation, and Trade Act of 1990, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624","children":[],"tail":", to which the amendment relates, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/237/s1101/b/4"},"text":"section 1101(b)(4) of Pub. L. 102–237","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1421"},"text":"section 1421 of Title 7","children":[],"tail":", Agriculture."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"iddcd2336e-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section effective thirty days after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1985-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1985","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/205/s401"},"text":"section 401 of Pub. L. 99–205","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date of 1985 Amendment note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2001"},"text":"section 2001 of thi